277
00:21:55,980 --> 00:21:57,020
What do you mean?

278
00:21:59,020 --> 00:22:00,050
The vice-director...

279
00:22:00,689 --> 00:22:01,949
Woo Seung Hui...

280
00:22:03,689 --> 00:22:05,419
created another bait.

281
00:22:11,429 --> 00:22:13,699
Could you tell me in detail?

282
00:22:14,629 --> 00:22:15,740
Gosh.

283
00:22:16,340 --> 00:22:19,409
Woo Seung Hui left the academy with Hye Jin's class materials?

284
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:22,609
