287
00:22:28,510 --> 00:22:30,350
"Look how evil Woo Seung Hui is."

288
00:22:30,520 --> 00:22:32,080
That's basically saying,

289
00:22:33,520 --> 00:22:35,119
"Ms. Seo is ruined beyond repair."

290
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:36,659
"She's got nothing."

291
00:22:37,820 --> 00:22:38,990
You know?

292
00:22:40,330 --> 00:22:41,359
Gosh.

293
00:22:51,439 --> 00:22:52,570
Aren't you scared?

294
00:22:54,770 --> 00:22:56,639
You said you really wanted to teach in this neighborhood.

295
00:22:57,909 --> 00:22:59,209
