296
00:23:01,350 --> 00:23:02,580
I have people backing up.

297
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:06,389
The kids like me.

298
00:23:07,449 --> 00:23:09,119
They will like me wherever I end up.

299
00:23:10,189 --> 00:23:11,260
Ms. Nam.

300
00:23:12,889 --> 00:23:13,889
You're cool.

301
00:23:19,530 --> 00:23:20,730
Gosh.

302
00:23:22,669 --> 00:23:23,840
Goodness.

303
00:23:24,500 --> 00:23:27,209
Are they Woo Seung Hui's archenemies or something?

304
00:23:31,939 --> 00:23:33,649
Why do you keep looking around?

305
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:35,050
Oh, nothing.

306
00:23:35,379 --> 00:23:38,149
