307
00:23:41,949 --> 00:23:45,290
This is why I always had a soft spot for you, Ms. Kim.

308
00:23:46,230 --> 00:23:48,159
You're cute and innocent.

309
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,859
That's why you get along with your students well.

310
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:53,969
Well, I don't have to talk about how you're the prettiest teacher.

311
00:23:54,300 --> 00:23:56,600
Well, I wouldn't say I'm the prettiest teacher.

312
00:23:57,369 --> 00:23:59,340
Lee Jun Ho has low standards. That's all.

313
00:23:59,409 --> 00:24:01,669
Seo Hye Jin is nothing compared to you.

314
00:24:02,939 --> 00:24:06,609
