324
00:24:37,439 --> 00:24:39,149
You don't have class today. Why are you here?

325
00:24:39,850 --> 00:24:40,909
To study.

326
00:24:42,379 --> 00:24:44,250
I wonder why you even bother to lie when it's so obvious.

327
00:24:47,320 --> 00:24:48,689
You're waiting for Mr. Lee Myeong Jun, right?

328
00:24:49,159 --> 00:24:50,859
You've been glancing at his desk.

329
00:24:53,689 --> 00:24:54,760
I knew it.

330
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:57,000
I can't fool you.

331
00:24:59,030 --> 00:25:00,629
Are you upset that you couldn't kill him off yesterday?

332
00:25:00,869 --> 00:25:02,100
Will you finish him today?

333
00:25:04,939 --> 00:25:05,939
Yes.

334
00:25:06,040 --> 00:25:07,570
Gosh. The road is so slippery.

335
00:25:09,340 --> 00:25:10,510
Good morning.

336
00:25:10,840 --> 00:25:12,609
- Are you preparing for your class? - Yes.

337
00:25:12,909 --> 00:25:15,409
I knew it. You're nothing without a backbone.

338
00:25:16,020 --> 00:25:17,580
Whatever happens to her...

339
00:25:19,090 --> 00:25:20,149
Is this the power of love?

340
00:25:24,659 --> 00:25:27,230
I'll call the ambulance. Make sure to finish him this time.

341
00:25:38,300 --> 00:25:39,369
What?

342
00:25:44,280 --> 00:25:45,340
What do you want?

343
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:53,350
You know, I had always wanted to point this out.

344
00:25:53,919 --> 00:25:56,659
But your attitude toward your senior instructors...

345
00:25:57,060 --> 00:25:58,659
