346
00:26:00,689 --> 00:26:01,830
Is that so?

347
00:26:03,959 --> 00:26:05,000
I didn't know.

348
00:26:07,830 --> 00:26:11,240
Yes. So if you need to talk to your senior instructor,

349
00:26:11,699 --> 00:26:13,869
you must be polite and approach him sensibly.

350
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:17,709
Be polite and approach sensibly.

351
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,919
Is there anything else I can fix?

352
00:26:24,980 --> 00:26:26,050
