357
00:26:44,800 --> 00:26:46,570
I apologize for my immature thoughts...

358
00:26:48,409 --> 00:26:49,439
and actions.

359
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:55,679
See?

360
00:26:56,280 --> 00:26:58,050
You don't know the first thing about a proper apology.

361
00:26:58,219 --> 00:26:59,649
That's not how you apologize.

362
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:03,060
You must clearly state what you did wrong,

363
00:27:03,419 --> 00:27:05,459
how you inconvenienced the other party,

364
00:27:05,619 --> 00:27:06,990
what you reflected on,

365
00:27:07,389 --> 00:27:09,129
and how you would take responsibility for it.

366
00:27:09,359 --> 00:27:11,030
These are the things you must specify.

367
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:13,570
I talked down to you.

368
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,730
I insulted you by using my students.

369
00:27:16,469 --> 00:27:17,570
I apologize for that.

370
00:27:18,369 --> 00:27:19,510
I should have...

371
00:27:20,209 --> 00:27:22,510
explained everything after calmly listening to your opinion.

372
00:27:24,139 --> 00:27:25,850
But I only focused on how wronged I felt.

373
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:29,750
Ms. Seo and I...

374
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:33,090
didn't think how it could cause a misunderstanding for everyone.

375
00:27:35,219 --> 00:27:37,919
From now on, before I act on anything,

376
00:27:40,060 --> 00:27:41,859
I will be polite, use a sensible approach,

377
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:46,399
and seek advice from my senior instructors.

378
00:27:49,169 --> 00:27:50,270
So you've been reflecting?

379
00:27:50,899 --> 00:27:51,969
To my core.

380
00:27:54,869 --> 00:27:55,909
Well, then.

381
00:27:57,810 --> 00:27:59,480
I don't hold a grudge or anything.

382
00:28:03,219 --> 00:28:05,449
Get back to work. I must prepare for my class.

383
00:28:14,060 --> 00:28:15,129
Right.

384
00:28:17,730 --> 00:28:18,959
I sent you an email.

385
00:28:20,070 --> 00:28:21,070
What email?

386
00:28:22,129 --> 00:28:23,199
You should check.

387
00:28:35,209 --> 00:28:38,280
(To Lee Myeong Jun, from Lee Jun Ho)

388
00:28:38,320 --> 00:28:39,919
The college entrance exam, the mock exams,

389
00:28:40,290 --> 00:28:41,619
the texts from the city and provincial offices of education,

390
00:28:42,149 --> 00:28:43,689
analysis on literature and linguistic understanding,

391
00:28:44,490 --> 00:28:46,590
and the background information of the selected non-fiction texts.

392
00:28:48,030 --> 00:28:49,729
I summarized them while making my study materials.

393
00:28:49,730 --> 00:28:52,330
There's still room for improvement, but you'll find some use for them.

394
00:28:54,770 --> 00:28:57,000
What was that? I thought you were going to finish him.

395
00:29:00,810 --> 00:29:02,879
Did you plant some kind of virus in the email?

396
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:05,080
Don't you have a class to teach?

397
00:29:07,879 --> 00:29:08,949
I do.

398
00:29:21,389 --> 00:29:23,260
Did Mr. Lee get up on the wrong side of the bed today?

399
00:29:23,859 --> 00:29:25,500
It hurt my pride just watching him.

400
00:29:26,199 --> 00:29:28,469
I'll relay the message. I'm sure he'll be happy to hear that.

401
00:29:53,359 --> 00:29:54,359
What was that?

402
00:29:58,060 --> 00:29:59,570
I'm not that dense.

403
00:29:59,770 --> 00:30:01,030
What are you plotting?

404
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:06,240
Nothing.

405
00:30:06,869 --> 00:30:08,239
I'm truly reflecting on what I did.

406
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:09,280
What's your goal?

407
00:30:16,219 --> 00:30:17,780
Make it quick. I have a class.

408
00:30:19,020 --> 00:30:21,590
Given what happened, what could I possibly want?

409
00:30:25,459 --> 00:30:26,590
But there's one thing I can try.

410
00:30:28,659 --> 00:30:30,600
Trying to get as many instructors as possible to stay here.

411
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:32,969
If I can do that,

412
00:30:33,770 --> 00:30:35,429
I would even crawl under your legs.

413
00:30:36,570 --> 00:30:38,539
Why would you do that? I don't need you to do that.

414
00:30:38,540 --> 00:30:39,869
Then tell me what you need.

415
00:30:40,810 --> 00:30:42,368
Ms. Seo's career is going down anyway.

416
00:30:42,369 --> 00:30:43,639
Anyone can rise to become the ace of the academy.

417
00:30:44,540 --> 00:30:46,280
Our academy needs a new leader.

418
00:30:47,609 --> 00:30:49,919
Choisun Academy has been focusing on Korean for 20 years.

419
00:30:50,550 --> 00:30:52,418
Choisun Academy is known to have top-tier instructors.

420
00:30:52,419 --> 00:30:54,388
Instead of competing against them, you should just...

421
00:30:54,389 --> 00:30:55,590
Are you a partial owner of the academy?

422
00:30:56,219 --> 00:30:57,290
Why are you going this far?

423
00:30:59,629 --> 00:31:01,730
I like Ms. Seo a lot.

424
00:31:04,060 --> 00:31:05,399
What the...

425
00:31:05,730 --> 00:31:07,428
Her causing the academy to shut down...

426
00:31:07,429 --> 00:31:08,629
and the instructors to lose their jobs?

427
00:31:09,939 --> 00:31:11,699
I don't want her to live with that guilt.

428
00:31:15,669 --> 00:31:17,079
There isn't a lot of time,

429
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:19,649
and other academies are ready to welcome high school freshmen.

430
00:31:20,449 --> 00:31:22,080
Every year, there's always a wave of fresh students.

431
00:31:22,580 --> 00:31:25,179
There isn't a better time to change your reputation.

432
00:31:26,649 --> 00:31:29,149
I've been in this field way longer than you.

433
00:31:29,389 --> 00:31:30,820
Don't patronize me with basic facts.

434
00:31:32,260 --> 00:31:33,260
I apologize.

435
00:31:52,379 --> 00:31:53,510
You'd better be here...

436
00:31:54,010 --> 00:31:56,010
because you're prepared to the point...

437
00:31:56,280 --> 00:31:58,050
