438
00:32:00,619 --> 00:32:03,689
More than 100 students jumped academies at once.

439
00:32:04,060 --> 00:32:05,119
Right.

440
00:32:05,619 --> 00:32:08,389
That means you should be exceptionally busy.

441
00:32:10,159 --> 00:32:11,530
The files on the students...

442
00:32:12,060 --> 00:32:13,570
