443
00:32:15,429 --> 00:32:17,000
For that, you should be grateful.

444
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:20,310
We're letting you focus only on your class.

445
00:32:22,879 --> 00:32:24,340
The scandal regarding Ms. Seo and Mr. Lee.

446
00:32:25,580 --> 00:32:26,810
Were you the one who...

447
00:32:29,820 --> 00:32:30,919
I'd like to know.

448
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:38,520
I do not discuss business...

449
00:32:38,760 --> 00:32:40,230
