456
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,750
I'll be in touch.

457
00:33:02,879 --> 00:33:04,948
I'm sorry I couldn't have lunch with you.

458
00:33:04,949 --> 00:33:07,790
It's all right. I'm sure you have a lot of people to meet.

459
00:33:08,050 --> 00:33:09,050
Right.

460
00:33:09,490 --> 00:33:11,290
- I'll get going. - Sure.

461
00:33:13,129 --> 00:33:15,530
- Take care. - You too.

462
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:29,168
It seems as though Lee Jun Ho...

463
00:33:29,169 --> 00:33:30,379
