464
00:33:31,540 --> 00:33:33,550
(Daechi Chase)

465
00:33:35,679 --> 00:33:36,780
I'll talk to him.

466
00:33:37,179 --> 00:33:38,850
Just make sure to gather all my things,

467
00:33:39,520 --> 00:33:41,389
and reset my computer.

468
00:33:50,530 --> 00:33:51,600
That's who...

469
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:53,969
Woo Seung Hui is.

