00:33:55,530 --> 00:33:58,600
The thoughts one keeps buried deep inside?

471
00:33:59,300 --> 00:34:02,340
She has a knack for sniffing out the musty scent they give off.

472
00:34:10,719 --> 00:34:12,119
Lee Myeong Jun is one...

473
00:34:13,250 --> 00:34:15,020
