00:34:21,190 --> 00:34:23,159
(Lee Myeong Jun, Korean)

475
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:30,469
(Lee Jun Ho, Korean)

476
00:34:51,589 --> 00:34:54,429
(Vice-director Woo Seung Hui)

