505
00:36:19,650 --> 00:36:20,809
- Paraphrasing. - Paraphrasing.

506
00:36:20,810 --> 00:36:23,080
Right. It's like restating the text.

507
00:36:23,150 --> 00:36:25,750
Vocabulary and reading comprehension are vital tools.

508
00:36:25,819 --> 00:36:27,549
